solutions.content:
Simple solution:
1. Count number of zeros.
2. Iterate from end of the array,
	a. Calculate index where current element needs to be shifted.
	b. Shift current element if index lies within array.
	c. Check if current element is zero:
		i. Assign zero to (index-1) to duplicate zero if (index-1) lies within array.
		ii. Decrease zero counter by 1.

