we need to add one duplicate zero followed by original one
so we will use, for loop to check for zeroes,and 
we will use extra space ArrayList just to add element of arr and extra zeroes, 

   if element is non zero we will add it as it is
   else we will add extra zero to our ArrayList

    after above operation we will get ArrayList as {1,0,0,2,3,0,0,4,5,0,0};
    and we will also replace element at index i in arr with element at index i on ArrayList;
    arr[i]=ll.get(i);

so we will get updated arr ={1,0,0,2,3,0,0,4};  

